import React from 'react' import { ProductItem } from '../models/ProductModels' import { currencyFormatter } from './utilities/currencyFormatter' interface ApiProductsType { item: ProductItem } const ApiProducts: React.FC = ({item}) => { return (

{item.tag}

{item.articleNumber}

{item.name}

{item.description}

{item.category}

{currencyFormatter(item.price)}

Rating: {item.rating}

{item.imageName}

) } export default ApiProducts
